The package boost-smart-ptr is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS smart_ptr)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::smart_ptr)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_smart_ptr REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::smart_ptr)
